# DataSift clients, command line API specification

-a
--auth username:api_key
-e
--endpoint [core|push|historics|preview|sources]
-c
--command [endpoint specific subcommand e.g. compile for -e core]
-p
--param [command specific param e.g. id 12345]

# Response
The client is to print a JSON object with the response in the format

{
 "status" : 200,
 "headers" : {"X-rate-limit": 10000},
 "body" : {}
}
